WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Since you're sleepy, go to sleep.

2
00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:05.220
You're sleeping here tonight?

3
00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:08.180
Or what, Mrs. Huo?

4
00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:12.280
Just... just sleep?

5
00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:15.260
If you don't want to do anything else,

6
00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:16.940
just go to sleep quickly.

7
00:00:18.380 --> 00:00:18.940
Okay.

8
00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:29.260
Huo Jiu Ling.

9
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.040
You just said,

10
00:00:31.220 --> 00:00:32.240
you agreed to let me go to school.

11
00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:35.160
Weren't you just asleep?

12
00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:37.480
I was pretending just now.

13
00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:39.140
So tomorrow I can really

14
00:00:39.140 --> 00:00:40.440
go to school?

15
00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:45.920
If you're that upset, you can go.

16
00:00:58.660 --> 00:00:59.060
Madam.

17
00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:01.020
Sir has something to do,

18
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.420
he went out early this morning.

19
00:01:03.060 --> 00:01:04.380
He told us to send you

20
00:01:04.380 --> 00:01:05.360
to school for your advanced class today.

21
00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.280
They will be responsible for sending you to school,

22
00:01:08.540 --> 00:01:09.700
keeping you safe.

23
00:01:10.660 --> 00:01:12.840
When can I be a little free?

24
00:01:12.940 --> 00:01:13.660
I'm so frustrated!

